strings: <voice_0x01000FF1><se_low>Yangus: Here 'e is! You ain't gonna slip away this time! Put 'em up, Dhoulmagus!

<voice_0x01000FF2><se_def>Angelo: There's nowhere for you to run now.
We've got you cornered.

<voice_0x01000FF3><se_high>Jessica: I made a promise to my brother...
You'll pay for what you did!

<voice_0x01000FF4><se_def>Angelo: We've caught up with you now!
You can't get out of this one, Dhoulmagus!

<voice_0x01000FF5><se_high>Jessica: You murdered my brother!
I won't let you out of here alive!

<voice_0x01000FF6><se_high>Jessica: Now I've found you!
Right, Dhoulmagus!
This is for Alistair!
<voice_0x01000FF7><se_high>Jessica: I hope you like it here, because you're about to become a permanent fixture!
